Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.02,0:00:05.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kingdom of Fiore...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.24,0:00:09.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A neutral country of 17 million people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:12.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a world of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:15.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic is bought and sold there every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:18.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is an integral part of people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:23.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are those who use magic as their occupation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:27.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those people are referred to as wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:34.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The wizards belong to various guilds \Nand perform jobs on commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:38.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a large number of guilds within the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:43.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And in a certain city there lies a certain guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:49.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A guild from which various legends were once born... Or \Nrather, will continue to be born long into the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:51.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And its name is:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:55.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.39,0:00:57.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:01:06.71,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gather all the light, and shine down on your tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:16.13,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Can you hear this voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:21.05,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! It's hoarse from yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.05,0:01:25.37,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Until your heart can hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:29.48,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:34.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon and sun high-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:39.18,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're not forgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:44.58,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're not here to make me laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:47.72,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,even what I'm looking for can't be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:51.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Snowing, be honest with yourself and smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:56.73,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,because when two people lay close, time overlaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:58.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:07.65,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gather all the light, and shine down on your tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:12.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:27.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Last time on Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:29.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:31.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:33.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:35.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So these are Fairy Tail wizards?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:37.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:38.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:39.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza? You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:41.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest wizard in Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:43.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this, basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:47.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Happy back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:51.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:52.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lullaby?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:56.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-chan, three beers over this way, if you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:58.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:00.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, go out on a date with me, Mira-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:02.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't start with {\i1}this{\i0} again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:04.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:09.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a wife, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:11.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop that, Mira-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:13.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One of these days I'd like to drink in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:15.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You drink too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:17.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to do some job sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:19.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye. We're running out of food money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:22.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I wish we had that 2,000,000 jewel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:25.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, I'm not going\N to make my rent for next month!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:27.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to do a job, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:32.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Armored Wizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:38.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Looking for a magic bracelet..." {yes, I know it's written "bracelet of magic" on the wall, but I'll consider Lucy abbreviating}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:40.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dispel the magic on this cursed cane..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:42.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fortune Telling using Astrology."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:44.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Monster Hunt in a volcano?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:48.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There sure are a lot of things wizards are requested to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:51.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If one suits your fancy, just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:54.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master is off at the regular meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:55.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Regular meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:04:00.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All the guild masters in the area get \Ntogether and give regular reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:02.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's different than the council meetings, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:05.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Reedus, can I borrow a light pen? {Reedus has a "Oui" there inbetween these lines.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:06.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oui.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:08.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The light pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:12.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A magic item that allows you to write in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:18.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The people on top of the world of magic are the 10 members \Nof the council, connected with the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:22.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their job is to bring order to everything \Nthat goes on in the world of magic. {edit: "order" twice in the sentence}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:27.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And on the chance that a wizard commits \Na crime, they pass judgment on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:33.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then below them are the organization of guild \Nmasters, the Guild Master Leagues.  {choice of league from text on screen}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:36.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They circulate the decrees of the council,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:42.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,smooth out communication between the guilds \Nin the same area, and keep us unified.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pretty tough job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:48.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea that the guilds were connected like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:51.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping the guilds in alliance is very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:53.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:56.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those dark guys are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:01.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:02.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:06.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those "dark guys" really exist.  Dark guilds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning, guilds that don't belong to the league.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:13.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys sometimes have their hands \Nin illegal, villainous activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:16.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, hurry up and pick a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:19.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And who are you to tell me that, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:21.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause we're a team, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:23.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We picked the last job ourselves, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This time it's your turn, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:26.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:29.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our team is history, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:33.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd didn't care as long as it was some blond girl, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:34.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:38.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I chose you, Lucy... because you're cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:41.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:45.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to lock it down now. \NYou'll get more team requests than you can stomach soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:47.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:48.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuddap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:51.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just tell me to shuddap, you flamer! {this line's timing seemed to come in rather late--I have no problem with the translation, though} {okay, I'm getting a bit creative on the insults...}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:53.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause your blabbin's pissin' me off, porn star!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Birdbrain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:55.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Slippery bastard! {referring to his ice?  Or his skin?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:57.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You stink! {yep.} {I think?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:57.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:01.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, how about the two of us form the team of love?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight. Just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:08.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I must gaze at you through sunglasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:12.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I took them off, I'd go blind for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:13.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:16.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait... You're a Celestial Wizard?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:17.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:20.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She's got, like, a cow and a crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:22.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate, what cruel tricks you play on me! {edit: Unless you really want to do "thou playest." Actually, Loke's a charmer, but not really a character who would be stuck with archaic, Shakespeare-like language}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:26.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! We're going to end it here for now! {edit: used "end" to play off Lucy's "start" joke}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:27.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we start something in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:30.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke has issues with Celestial Wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:33.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a rumor that he had some women trouble a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:34.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, figures...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:40.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you guys give it a rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:43.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He picked this fight! You think I'm not gonna pay him back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:44.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then put on some clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:47.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who provoked me, droopy eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:51.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When exactly did I provoke you, squinty eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking underpants!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:53.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dimwit! {if you want to add in extra pun, use "dimlit" :)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:54.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's third-grader time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:04.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:07.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:14.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza-san... Natsu mentioned her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:18.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'd be correct to call her the strongest \Nfemale wizard in all of Fairy Tail right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:23.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Erza's footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:28.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza's comin' back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:32.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With this kind of reaction, Erza-san \Nreally must be an amazing wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:35.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:46.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Master here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:53.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back. Master is at the regular meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:54.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:56.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza-san, what is that giant thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:07:59.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The horn of the monster I defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:03.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The locals decorated it and gave it to me as a souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:03.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a problem with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:06.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:09.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Think she knows about the incident on Mt. Hakobe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Crap, I'm dead meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:13.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's quite different than what I'd imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:15.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:17.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a bunch of rumors while I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:21.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About how Fairy Tail keeps causing problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:24.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master might forgive you, but I will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:25.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:27.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you drink in such an undignified manner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:28.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Visitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:28.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:30.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your dancing outside. {edit: shortened for time}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:31.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wakaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:32.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dropping ash on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:33.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nab!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:37.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hesitating in front of the Request Board as usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:38.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a job! {This becomes a running joke. Nab is always looking for the job that "only he can do" so he hangs around doing nothing}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:39.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Macao!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.53,0:08:44.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:46.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you all give me such trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:48.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let it slide today without saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:51.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed like she said plenty already...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:52.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she like a disciplinary committee or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:53.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:57.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she has a sharp tongue, but she looks human enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:59.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she really all that scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:01.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are Natsu and Gray here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:02.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.63,0:09:06.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Erza. The both of us are getting along great today, as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:07.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu's acting like Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:14.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Well, even the best of friends fight at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:18.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I like it most seeing the two of you get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:19.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, best friends is a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:20.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:22.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen Natsu like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:27.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu challenged Erza to a fight before and was beat to a pulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:29.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Natsu? {"Natsu was what?" didn't read well somehow}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:32.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Gray got beat to a pulp \Nwhen she saw him walking about naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.87,0:09:36.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When Loke courted Erza, she beat him to a pulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:38.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He reaped what he sowed, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:40.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so she's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:43.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, Gray, I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.94,0:09:48.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a troubling story after I finished this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:54.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly speaking, this is something for Master to decide, \Nbut I want to settle it quickly so I decided myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want the two of you to lend me your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:09:59.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:02.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza asked the two of them for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:04.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This has never happened before...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:06.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a team...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:10.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:12.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, Natsu, and Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:15.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have imagined it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:20.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But this might be Fairy Tail's ultimate team!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:25.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:28.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnolia Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:33.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd I have to be stuck with {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:38.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If Erza wants help, I can handle that by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:40.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then go by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:41.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:45.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then stay home, and get beaten up by Erza afterwards! {edit: I know you were using a theme of "beat to a pulp" but the phrase seemed to confuse the subtitle}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:48.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}And why do you always walk around with that bedroll?  {bedroll seems fine to me.} {maybe leave it as "futon"... but futon has a different meaning in English than the bedroll thing here.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:47.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretend we don't know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:48.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretend we don't know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:50.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:51.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}So I have something to sleep on, duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:52.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Mira-san said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:56.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are totally going to fight when Erza isn't looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:57.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So please stop them, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:58.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:00.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not stopping them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:04.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize. Were you waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:06.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:08.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice packing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:11.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot of luggage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.24,0:11:13.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get along together today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:14.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:16.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And here comes Happy #2!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:19.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Getting along is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:20.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:23.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you were at Fairy Tail yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:25.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the new recruit, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:28.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-san asked that I come along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:30.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Erza. Glad to have you on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:35.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so {\i1}you're{\i0} Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:39.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who defeated the guerrilla \Nmercenaries with just one finger, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:41.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have my thanks for offering to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:42.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:46.76,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite different from what actually happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:46.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Glad to be of service...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:49.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, I have one condition for coming along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:50.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:52.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:55.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When we get back, fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:57.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, think it over! {It's "hayamaru na!" Don't rush into anything. Not "ayamaru." "Hayamaru na!" is a standard phrase one uses on people attempting to commit suicide}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:11:58.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a death wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:01.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't go the same as last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:05.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good enough to beat you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:09.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that you have improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:12.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not confident by any means, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:12.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:14.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:19.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm all fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:26.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:28.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how you get after picking a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:31.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It happens every time, though.  Must be tough on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:32.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:33.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, sit next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:34.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:36.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're telling me to move?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:40.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:41.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:44.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This way it's a bit easier on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:45.49,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretending not to see
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:48.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she is definitely a bit weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:51.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, isn't it about time you told us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:53.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we supposed to be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:58.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our opponents are the dark guild, Eisenwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:02.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They intend to do mischief with some magic called "Lullaby."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:03.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lullaby?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:04.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, those guys from before...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The dark guild, Eisenwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:14.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems we got a message from Kageyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.05,0:13:17.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He finally got that "item" we've been wanting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:19.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our time has finally come. {edit: "chance is better used on the next line than this one}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:24.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our only chance to accomplish our objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:29.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, while those old geezer guild masters \Nare having their regular meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:41.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you also met some members of Eisenwald?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:43.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they did say something about a lullaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:45.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistaking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:49.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They were refugees from Eisenwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:52.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect they didn't want to follow the plan and were escaping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:54.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this plan has something to do with Lullaby?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:56.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I would imagine so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.74,0:14:01.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That shadow that snatched them up was probably \Na member of Eisenwald's main force.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:04.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They had to make a move to keep their plans from leaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:06.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What could they be planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:09.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:12.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the way back from my previous job...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:17.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At the town of Onibas, I stopped at a bar where wizards gather. {Your characterization of Erza (and mine, for that matter) keeps her well spoken. It seems a little out of character for her to end sentences with a preposition unless there is no other choice}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:19.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's the booze?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:21.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe down already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:23.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:27.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally found the place Lullaby was hidden, but that damn seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:28.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a damned clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:29.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your voice down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:31.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to get upset about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:35.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle the rest myself, so you go back to the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:36.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Koge-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:37.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you'll be fine alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:43.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Erigor-san I'll be back with the lullaby in three days, tops.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:47.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lullaby... Like, a song to get children to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:53.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the seal he was talking about was \Nthought to be quite a strong spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:55.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So they were also part of Eisenwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:59.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But I foolishly didn't think of it at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:02.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or the name Erigor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:06.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The top ace of the dark guild Eisenwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:11.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erigor, who's nicknamed "shinigami" since \Nhe only takes assassination requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:12.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Assassinations?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:17.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally assassination requests are banned by the council.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:20.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Eisenwald wanted money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:23.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so six years ago they were thrown out of the Wizard's Guild League.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:28.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However they don't listen to orders and have continued to operate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:31.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:33.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking juicy all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:34.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:36.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in error.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.77,0:15:43.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had noticed the name Erigor back then I would have forced \Nthem to suffer and made them tell me their plans! {edit: again, with your characterization of Erza, "world of hurt" seems a little out of place}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:43.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:45.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:49.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eisenwald is planning to do something with this Lullaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:52.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's definitely something evil, so you want to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:53.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.86,0:16:00.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not feel as if I can oppose an entire guild on \Nmy own, and that is why I asked for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:03.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading straight into Eisenwald!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:05.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:06.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:07.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I hadn't come...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:09.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy's juicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:10.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:13.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, give me a discount!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:18.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what kind of magic do you use, Erza-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:19.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just call me Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:22.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza's magic is really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her opponent's blood goes everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:26.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:29.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think your magic is prettier than mine, Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:31.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:40.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:43.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so {\i1}that's{\i0} why you two don't get along?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:46.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Natsu uses flame and you use ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:47.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:48.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:51.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Onibus Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:54.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those guys from Eisenwald still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:57.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. But I came here to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:17:00.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a wild goose chase to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:02.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:07.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He departed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so busy telling the story, I forgot about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:12.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:14.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I know he's bad with transportation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:17.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, would someone hit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:18.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:23.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:26.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're a wizard in one of those legal guilds?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:28.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:34.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Legal guilds ain't all they're cracked up to be, Fairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:37.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Know what we call you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:39.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Flies! Yes, flies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:43.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:45.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's with that magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:50.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:57.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is how you use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:58.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:10.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now look here, you can't just go pulling the emergency lever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:12.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for my ally, please understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:14.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.93,0:18:17.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please bring our luggage to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:18.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:23.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All the people at Fairy Tail are like this, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:24.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:26.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then where are your clothes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:29.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:31.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:33.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:34.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:37.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did a nice one on me back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:41.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard Shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:46.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap... Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:48.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,High Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:51.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that emergency stop was a false alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:53.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will be departing shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:54.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I'm outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:56.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait right there, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:59.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away with hurting a member of Eisenwald!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:04.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're one of those Eisenwald guys? You \Ntalked a lot of trash about Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:07.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's finish this outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:11.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A magic-driven four-wheeler.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:14.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It consumes the magic of the driver to increase speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.73,0:19:24.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:25.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:28.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt, jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:31.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You left me behind, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:34.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That we did. At least you're unhurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:35.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:37.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:39.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, unhurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:40.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got into a fight with some weird guy on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:41.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some weird guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:45.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who grabbed those Happy-eaters in the forest. {edit: having "grabbed" and "captured" in the same sentence seems to make it confusing}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:46.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was part of Eisenwald or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:48.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:51.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eisenwald are the people we're after!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.07,0:19:52.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you let him escape from under your nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:54.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I heard about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:56.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I explained just a moment ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:58.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to people when they're talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:00.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that's because she knocked him unconscious...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:02.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's totally amazing in so many different ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:03.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:04.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Erza for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:08.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was on that train, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:09.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go after him immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:13.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing stood out to me, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.41,0:20:14.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! {edit: This is Natsu's line}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:16.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He had this flute shaped like a skull
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:18.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a skull with three eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:19.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A three-eyed skull?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:21.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some bad taste there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:23.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:26.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know about that flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:29.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lullaby... The song of curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:31.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:32.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:34.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Song of curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:35.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean like, a magic song?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:38.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only read about them in books,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:42.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but one of the forbidden magics is the curse of death, right? {edit: the topic of Forbidden Magics comes up again and again. If you want to used "banned" that's fine, but it should be used consistantly. (I used the word "Forbidden" in the manga.)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:47.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. A black-magic curse that saps the \Nlife out of the person it's cast upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:50.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lullaby is even worse! {edit: Again, Lucy provides the background because she's a reader.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.84,0:20:56.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This train is the property of Eisenwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.03,0:20:57.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunugi Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.22,0:21:02.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone off, drivers and luggage too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.45,0:21:04.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Resist and you forfeit your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:06.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erigor-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:07.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kageyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:13.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you'd be coming back on this train, but looking \Nat the destruction... Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:15.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk about that later. First, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.84,0:21:19.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to lift the seal somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:22.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:25.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the forbidden Lullaby? {if you decided to use "banned," you should use it here too.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:31.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This flute was originally nothing but a tool used for death curses...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:37.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the great black wizard Zeref transformed \Nit even further into a demon flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:44.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All those who hear the sound of this flute have the life sucked \Nout of them. The mass-death curse magic, Lullaby!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:50.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going too fast, Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:53.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's you, don't underestimate the \Namount of magic it'll drain from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:56.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have that kind of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:22:00.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If Erigor gets his hands on that mass-death curse magic, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:03.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no telling what he'd do!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.48,0:22:09.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him... What's he after?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.55,0:22:15.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin! Start the operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.01,0:22:28.81,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me away to someplace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.81,0:22:33.81,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ride on a tin horse, just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:36.67,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,(Go!Go! Let's go! Romance)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.67,0:22:44.26,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad that my beloved doll can't talk to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.26,0:22:46.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,(Go!Go! Let's go! Romance)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.63,0:22:51.89,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I think of you tears start to flow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:57.01,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a crybaby, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.01,0:22:59.66,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,In the moon (the moon) at night (at night)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:01.40,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always (I'm always)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:04.70,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,searching for the rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:07.38,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at a loss for words (Hey! Hey! Hey!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.38,0:23:09.93,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,so much it's like I'm under a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:13.17,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This love is a monologue
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.17,0:23:15.31,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,from which I'll never awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:17.82,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at a loss for words (Hey! Hey! Hey!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.82,0:23:20.54,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,since I've completely fallen in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:23.62,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what spell I could chant,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.62,0:23:25.76,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,to get through to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:29.71,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The perfect thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.06,0:23:33.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Spouting this and that,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.69,0:23:36.30,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I just love you like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.30,0:23:39.48,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,One day I want to be able to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:41.75,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,"I've arrived."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.75,0:23:45.27,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,My words of thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.25,0:23:54.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.44,0:23:58.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-san, is Erza a scary person?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:24:00.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.79,0:24:03.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.56,0:24:06.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although if you make her angry, she'll knock you about 10 meters,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.36,0:24:09.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,or pound you into the ground up to your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.36,0:24:12.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's plenty scary, personally...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.76,0:24:15.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Fairies in the Wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.96,0:24:18.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, you'll get used to it in no time, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.77,0:24:21.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu and Gray used to make her angry all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.61,0:24:24.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're predicting I'm going to make her angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.57,0:24:26.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
